      "content": "it's just so heavy. like, everyone says \"it'll get better\" or \"stay strong,\" but they don't get it. they don't live in this body. it feels so selfish to keep going just to endure this, you know? like there's no real \"win\" anymore. it just feels like the most logical, kind thing for myself would be to just find a way to be still. to have actual silence. do you think i'm being crazy for thinking that?",
